#OBJECTS
#12301
boulder~
the giant boulder~
A giant boulder obstructs you from moving any further.~
~
13 1073741824 0
0 0 0 0
1 0 0 1
> push_prog 100~
mea $n You press your hands up to the boulder and put all the strength you can muster into pushing...
mpechoar $n $n attempts to shove the boulder aside...
if str($n) < 22
mea $n You strain yourself beyond your abilities, but the boulder doesn't budge.
mpechoar $n can't manage to move the boulder.
else
mpe With a great crash, the boulder falls down the mountainside far below.
mpopenpassage 12309 12310 0
endif
~
